This is a bookmarklet that analyzes the content on the current page and
recommends a Content Security Policy based on the types of content it finds on
the page and the sources of that content. The implementation also takes into
account resources that are dynamically added to the page by JavaScript.

Usage:
1. Visit any web page in your browser.
2. Click the bookmarklet.
3. Observe the recommended Content Security Policy.

See Also:
http://brandon.sternefamily.net/posts/2010/10/content-security-policy-recommendation-bookmarklet/
